{"lang": "zh_CN", "eventid": "main_12", "eventName": "惊霆无声", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "12-15", "avgTag": "行动前", "storyName": "千疮百孔", "storyInfo": "经历了漫长岁月的变形者集群向年轻的女妖之主敞开了心扉。随着酒店的一场大火，诺伯特区的真正的乱局才终于开始。", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ibtownn", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magicchange", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这次是伊比利亚。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_178", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耐心些，女妖，我在这里的日子最难忘。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以为你不会喜欢那里。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_178", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那场灾难发生之前，我确实不喜欢伊比利亚。那些夸夸其谈和自以为是让我腻烦透了。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他们不懂得畏惧。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那么，那场灾难让你满足了吗？", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_178", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不是老红眼病那样的心理变态，灾难本身也没什么出奇，这片大地何时缺少过灾难？", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但那些生物让我着迷。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是听说过一些传闻，说实话，那些东西让我十分不安。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它们与我们过于迥异。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_178", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你认为我与你迥异吗，女妖？", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你应该知道，无论是哪种样子，都不是真正的我。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "源石在所有人的身上都留下了无可辩驳的烙印，它让你们以现有的样子在世间行走。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可它唯独忘记了变形者。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唯独我们仍然保存了最初生时的样子。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你会为你的纯洁自豪吗？", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_178", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不，当这个世界都已变了样子，纯洁又还有什么意义？", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只能追赶它带来的变化，我只能追赶你们。追赶你们所创造的一切。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我用尽了各种办法，我在伊比利亚发现了一个荒废的镇子，我住了进去。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我们住了进去。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我们让那座镇子重新运行起来，工作，交流，商业，交通......", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "两百个我组成了一个小镇。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道你至今都没有陷入疯狂，是你的幸运还是不幸。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_178", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，谁知道呢。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "总之，我在那里度过了印象深刻的一段时光，有那么多的事情要处理，我每天沉溺其中。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这给我带来了一种错觉，我们过得有意义。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，疲乏最终还是到来了，专注于琐事很有趣，但是就算把它们全部加起来，依然无法让我找到答案。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到我发现了它们，我听有的人称呼那些东西为“海嗣”。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我观察了它们很久。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它们让你想到了自己。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_178", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，论统一，我们超过了海嗣和它们的那些大群。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "无论分化为多少形貌，我们始终是统一的，而海嗣，它们只能选择投入大群。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，你知道吗，我羡慕它们。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它们只需要遵循本能就够了。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寻找食物，寻找养分，繁衍，进化。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或许，你刚刚所说的，“纯洁”这个词，应该放在它们身上。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我，我留在原地，看着这一切，看着那些多姿多彩的小生物把一片海草同化为它们的一员。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它们什么都不想，它们做自己该做的事。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我们呢，我们的本能是什么？我们又该做什么？", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女妖，你能给我们什么建议？", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在笑吗？", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，变形者，我并非在嘲笑你。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位可称最古老的王庭之主的变形者阁下，只是在寻找他生活的意义。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这很重要，这当然很重要，我只是没想过，站在我面前的，原来是个彷徨的哲学家。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_178", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你猜，我们在维多利亚的大学当了几年哲学教授？", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "对于你们而言，寻找意义是简单的，除去那极少部分存在，生命总可称得上短暂。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "为自己寻找到一个目标，用以填满这些时光没那么难。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我们不行。", "name": "“伊比利亚人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_178"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_mini02_victoria_street_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magicchange", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "无论是你的提议，还是特雷西斯的未来，我们都没什么兴趣。", "name": "变形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "对于我们而言，都是打发时间罢了。", "name": "变形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我们为什么要对这些转瞬即逝的东西抱有感情呢？", "name": "变形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我们几乎穷尽了一切可能，我们也几乎穷尽了一切乐趣。", "name": "变形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我开始可怜你了，变形者。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你发现了我们只是个喊着什么都没劲透了的老家伙。", "name": "变形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "知道这个秘密的人可不多。", "name": "变形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的几个朋友教过我一种愚蠢的游戏......", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，还是算了。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "说说吧，女妖，我们比你猜的要有兴趣。", "name": "变形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不过，或许得等等了，有个麻烦的工作找上门了。", "name": "变形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#3$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是在这里，但我们恐怕还是得分点心。", "name": "变形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#3$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g6_hotellobby", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没有......是什么意思？", "name": "阿米娅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没有就是没有，该死的！", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#3$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通讯站不在那里，那里什么也没有，有人抢先了！", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#3$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是那些深池的部队吗？", "name": "阿米娅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#15$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恐怕还要早得多。根据灰尘的厚度判断，诺伯特区刚驶离伦蒂尼姆的时候，就有人盯上那里了。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位赤铁近卫队的队长不会真的被我们骗过去的，他很快就会发现预计的通讯没有发出。", "name": "“灰礼帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但最起码，我们又回到同一条起跑线了，大家重新有了挣奖金的机会。", "name": "“灰礼帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "无论是服务于开斯特公爵的你，还是深池的鬼魂部队......", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你们都以秘密潜入的方式进入这个地块，这就说明了，你们想维持诺伯特区表面上的现状。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "无法逼迫公爵们的主力部队行动起来，我们的计划就没办法真正实现。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "别再用这套说辞了，戴菲恩。", "name": "伊内丝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要你的那位公爵母亲知道你还在这里，她就会想办法来救你的，对吧。", "name": "伊内丝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#5$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不能保证......", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#5$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "承认自己和母亲的关系不错没什么丢人的。", "name": "伊内丝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "你有办法吗，伊内丝？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line154"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很麻烦。", "name": "伊内丝"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#9$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"i