": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，真是折腾，这家酒店又乱了几分。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#7$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不亲自打扫的人，总是不知道保持一点秩序有多不容易。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#7$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "珀茜瓦尔！珀茜瓦尔！", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她又跑到哪里去了......", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#10$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，就让我这个老家伙自己待一会儿吧。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#10$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这位年迈的酒店经理找来了一张同样年迈的扶手椅，选了个舒服的姿势坐了进去。"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她......那个卡特斯女孩，就是魔王吗？", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#3$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "追上这些变化越来越难了，就连我都要为此吃惊。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#3$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "变化......变化，也许我怠惰于这种变化了吧。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#3$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "变化毕竟不是前进。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#3$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，也该告别这位老朋友了，说实话......我真的很喜欢这里。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#11$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉......考伯特该再坚持两个月的，谁能想到呢，两个月后，萨卡兹的军队进了城，一个魔族佬也能从清洁员变成酒店经理呢。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#10$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我总是弄不懂这些。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#10$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萨卡兹老人站起身来，巡视着酒店的大堂，这里的每一件物品都与他息息相关。"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那个叫伊内丝的卡普里尼说，战争不配用任何修饰。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#10$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那么，就让我们还原它本来的面貌吧。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#10$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_lighter", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在不知被多少政要贵族踏上过的精美编织地毯上，